// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0880 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 8543c65e-aa90-56d4-91ed-6e67e31e1c52

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*")
